OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773418281
OL,3,C'Worse than childbirth': A mother's
OL,4,Cwarning over rising ketamine use
OL,6,FThe event, organized by the charity
OL,7,FForward Trust, aimed to educate public
OL,8,Fservice workers on the severe impacts
OL,9,Fof the drug to ensure they are better
OL,10,Fequipped to help others.
OL,12,FSpeaking about her time in Margate
OL,13,Fduring the lockdown, Amy described how
OL,14,Fthe drug completely took over her
OL,15,Flife, leading her to cancel plans with
OL,16,Ffriends and even miss work.
OL,18,FCentral to her struggle were the
OL,19,Fsevere physical side effects known as
OL,20,F"k-cramps".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
