FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773418281
OL,3,C'Worse than childbirth': A mother's
OL,4,Cwarning over rising ketamine use
OL,6,FHe warned that many users are being
OL,7,F"written off" by the very systems
OL,8,Fdesigned to support them: "There's
OL,9,Fstill so much stigma and
OL,10,Fdiscrimination around people who use
OL,11,Fsubstances.
OL,13,F"I still go into meetings with housing
OL,14,Fofficers, local councils, who are
OL,15,Fpretty much writing people off.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
