FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773418281
OL,3,C'Worse than childbirth': A mother's
OL,4,Cwarning over rising ketamine use
OL,6,FDr. Olani Yiaajayi warned that the
OL,7,Feffects of the drug will eventually be
OL,8,Ffelt across every speciality of
OL,9,Fmedicine: "If we are able to prevent
OL,10,Fit becoming an epidemic, we might be
OL,11,Fable to get hold of it better".
OL,13,FThe hope for campaigners is that by
OL,14,Fhearing lived experiences like Amy's,
OL,15,Fthe local system will be better
OL,16,Fprepared the next time someone reaches
OL,17,Fout for help.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
